Package: siduction-art-gdm-@CODENAME_SAFE@
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    gdm
Description: GDM theme for siduction @VERSION@ release
 release specific artwork theme for the GDM display manager to be used in
 combination GTK2 based desktop environments like Xfce or LXDE.
 .
 GDM artwork for: siduction @VERSION@ (@CODENAME@)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

